nts, it provides a dynamical dark energy model of\ncosmology that satisfies the de Sitter swampland conjecture. We comment on a\nviable solution to overcome the tension between low- and high-redshift\nobservations within the AOV background and discuss the implications for the\nswampland program.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Nov 2019 17:26:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 15:23:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-29"}
