tion. An online time delay measurement\n& estimation procedure has been implemented and proposed in this research. We\nhave implemented an adaptive digital smith predictor using the online time\ndelay measurement and identification. The implemented smith predictor provides\ngood results for both intermediate node and point to point connection. An\nstability analysis of the DC motor system with variation of delay has been\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Dec 2019 06:54:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-10"}
