exemplified with real closed fields and\np-adically closed fields. The special radical is well-behaved with respect to\nlocalisation, and this leads to an equiresidual analogue of the prime spectrum,\nwhich connects affine EQAG with scheme theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Dec 2019 07:51:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2020 10:41:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 9 Jul 2022 08:02:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
